text: KKNB may refer to: * KKNB-LP, a low-power radio station (92.7 FM) licensed to serve Kanab, Utah, United States * KIBZ, a radio station (104.1 FM) licensed to serve Crete, Nebraska, United States, which held the call sign KKNB from 1988 to 2001 * Kanab Municipal Airport (ICAO code KKNB)
title: KKNB
